	<BusinessDocument name="Engineering Change Request" nameID="PIP2C2EngineeringChangeRequest" specificationLocation="urn:rosettanet:specification:interchange:EngineeringChangeRequest:xsd:schema:01.00">
		<Documentation>Contains the necessary information for a stakeholder to convey a need for consideration of engineering action. This document is simply a request for a possible engineering action and not an instruction for change.</Documentation>
	</BusinessDocument>
	<!--REM: Engineering Change Confirmation Document-->
	<BusinessDocument name="Engineering Change Confirmation" nameID="PIP2C2EngineeringChangeConfirmation" specificationLocation="urn:rosettanet:specification:interchange:EngineeringChangeConfirmation:xsd:schema:01.00">
		<Documentation>Contains the disposition for the requested engineering change. It contains the Engineering Change proprietary request number, response code that could be approve, reject or pending, and appropriate comments.</Documentation>
	</BusinessDocument>
